- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possible category as undecidability is a topic in computational complexity theory.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper deals with a specific computational model (Minsky machines).
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a less likely category, but still possible as linear logic has been used in some machine learning applications.
